40|$|Malignant pleural {{mesothelioma}} (MPM) {{is a highly}} aggressive cancer <b>of</b> <b>the</b> <b>pleura</b> with a well-established male predominance and causative link with asbestos exposure. We report four cases of female patients with MPM referred for palliation of symptoms thought {{to be due to}} previous non-pleural malignancy...|$|R
